<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Under Reconstruction | Ghana Competition Law & Policy Seminar</title>
    <meta content="Site is temporarily under reconstruction" name="description" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport" />
    <link href="https://ik.imagekit.io/dr5fryhth/conference/imglogo?updatedAt=1769778325875" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" />
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Neuemontreal';
            src: url('/assets/fonts/PPNeueMontreal-Regular.woff') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-display: swap;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Seasonmix';
            src: url('/assets/fonts/SeasonMix-Regular.woff') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-display: swap;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
        body, button, input { font-family: 'Neuemontreal', Arial, sans-serif; }
        body {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #1f2937;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }
        .logo img { height: 60px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }

        .lottie-wrap {
            width: 480px;
            height: 360px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Seasonmix', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .documents-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .documents-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .documents-desc {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        .doc-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .doc-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #1a365d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .doc-link:hover {
            background: #eef2ff;
            border-color: #c7d2fe;
        }
        .doc-link svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .footer a { color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none; }
        .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .subtitle { font-size: 0.95rem; }
            .documents-card { padding: 1.25rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/dr5fryhth/conference/imglogo?updatedAt=1769778325875" alt="CMC Ghana" />
        </div>

        <div class="lottie-wrap" id="lottieAnim"></div>

        <h1>Site Under Reconstruction</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">We are currently making improvements to our website. We'll be back soon with a better experience. In the meantime, you can access the seminar documents below or <a href="/feedback" style="color:#1a365d;font-weight:600;text-decoration:underline;">take our feedback survey</a>.</p>

        <div class="documents-card">
            <div class="documents-title">Seminar Documents</div>
            <div class="documents-desc">Download the materials from the Ghana Competition Law & Policy Seminar:</div>
            <div class="doc-list">
                <a href="/api/documents/competition-policy-and-law-concept" target="_blank" class="doc-link">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#1a365d" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                    Competition Policy and Law Concept
                </a>
                <a href="/api/documents/chairmans-remarks" target="_blank" class="doc-link">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#1a365d" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                    Chairman's Remarks
                </a>
                <a href="/api/documents/guest-speaker-speech" target="_blank" class="doc-link">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#1a365d" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                    Guest Speaker Speech
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/feedback" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1.5rem;padding:14px 32px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a365d 0%,#2d4a7c 100%);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;transition:all 0.2s;">Take the Feedback Survey</a>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Competition & Markets Center Ghana</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Questions? <a href="mailto:info@cmc-ghana.com">info@cmc-ghana.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lottie-web/5.12.2/lottie.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: document.getElementById('lottieAnim'),
            renderer: 'svg',
            loop: true,
            autoplay: true,
            path: '/lottie/maintenance.json'
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
